{
  "page": "Lord Penrose",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Penrose\" title=\"House Penrose\"><img alt=\"House Penrose.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/06/House_Penrose.svg/50px-House_Penrose.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/06/House_Penrose.svg/75px-House_Penrose.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/06/House_Penrose.svg/100px-House_Penrose.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Lord Penrose</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Penrose\" title=\"House Penrose\"><img alt=\"House Penrose.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/06/House_Penrose.svg/50px-House_Penrose.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/06/House_Penrose.svg/75px-House_Penrose.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/06/House_Penrose.svg/100px-House_Penrose.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nOld Penrose</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Parchments\" title=\"Lord of Parchments\">Lord of Parchments</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Penrose\" title=\"House Penrose\">House Penrose</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Stormlander\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Stormlander\">Stormlander</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Cortnay_Penrose\" title=\"Cortnay Penrose\">Cortnay Penrose</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Lord Penrose</b>, also known as <b>old Penrose</b>, is the Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Parchments\" title=\"Parchments\">Parchments</a> and the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Penrose\" title=\"House Penrose\">House Penrose</a>. His given name is unknown. He is the father of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Cortnay_Penrose\" title=\"Cortnay Penrose\">Cortnay Penrose</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Castellan\" title=\"Castellan\">castellan</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Storm%27s_End\" title=\"Storm&#39;s End\">Storm's End</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character\">Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Penrose&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Old Penrose is sickly and failing.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Penrose&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Penrose&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Although he has raised his banners for King <a href=\"/index.php/Renly_Baratheon\" title=\"Renly Baratheon\">Renly Baratheon</a>, Lord Penrose breaks bread with Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Davos_Seaworth\" title=\"Davos Seaworth\">Davos Seaworth</a> when he comes as a messenger from his liege lord, <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok0.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok0.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> treating the Onion Knight courteously.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The banners of House Penrose are seen in Renly's camp beneath <a href=\"/index.php/Bitterbridge\" title=\"Bitterbridge\">Bitterbridge</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Storm%27s_End_(299)\" title=\"Siege of Storm&#39;s End (299)\">siege of Storm's End</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Alester_Florent\" title=\"Alester Florent\">Alester Florent</a> urges Stannis to bring Lord Penrose to the castle and hang him in order to force the surrender of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Cortnay_Penrose\" title=\"Cortnay Penrose\">Cortnay Penrose</a>, the castellan of Storm's End and old Penrose's son.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Melisandre\" title=\"Melisandre\">Melisandre</a> instead sends a <a href=\"/index.php/Shadow_assassin\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Shadow assassin\">shadow</a> to assassinate Cortnay.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Penrose&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7